{"tid":2342084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[失物台][有圖]有冇人試過唔見銀包幾個月後仲揾得返？","createTime":"2020-12-26T23:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T15:03:01.000Z","uid":209274,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c366c96d59c4ef2c7439f2d9cdfb1910d8ab1687","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:31:10.000Z","msg":"真心一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為本人就係喺今年九月一號喺黃大仙至啟德一帶跌咗個charles &amp; keith白色銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全冇線索係喺地鐵站漏低咗定係喺啟德地盤附近跌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然當時已經即日報失，到而家都過咗三個月，應該都凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係銀包入面有好多重要嘅嘢，包括拎唔返嘅學生證仲有張貓貓嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都仲係心掛掛希望有日揾得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有神通廣大嘅連登巴絲執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔介意薄酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n附上銀包圖一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6AhxiP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6AhxiP.jpg&h=cd2c4f1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a42d994b46a80eed754c28c0670dd02a358665c1","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:34:18.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969f1ceafc8eb1b979d6942d20e39fbf35c3b5a6","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:35:03.000Z","msg":"樓豬正on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa37d522877c8eb1719005f2344a5360ffa36d67","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:36:19.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e459d2d3dc07850dc9f8dd288954eac7b91325a","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:36:43.000Z","msg":"好想揾返銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e09ca24d7661941ab6b17146937b93538dd72d","tid":2342084,"uid":325863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:38:05.000Z","msg":"出年先問可能更加有進展"},{"pid":"e9c0efd513f9de3a87084d946bf05fdafd04a13e","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91e09ca24d7661941ab6b17146937b93538dd72d","tid":2342084,"uid":325863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:38:05.000Z","msg":"出年先問可能更加有進展"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:39:25.000Z","msg":"好彩仲有幾日先到出年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c73f175db4c485db4f30513f52d6c13b457c5e1","tid":2342084,"uid":261330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"有，試過唔見咗半年之後個有心人先交返去我學校（入面有學生証）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要入面冇少過錢<br />\n諗緊係咪執到但成日唔記得要拎去我學校"},{"pid":"b23eb92b99a6876936069981ae62a68e8802fd31","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4c73f175db4c485db4f30513f52d6c13b457c5e1","tid":2342084,"uid":261330,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"有，試過唔見咗半年之後個有心人先交返去我學校（入面有學生証）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要入面冇少過錢<br />\n諗緊係咪執到但成日唔記得要拎去我學校"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:43:30.000Z","msg":"屋企人試過跌咗銀包，身份證都補領埋之後有人特登寄返曬啲卡俾佢，唯獨是係冇咗個銀包，信封上面個地址都係print出嚟而唔係手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早知我都喺銀包度寫低地址 哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52eb6ed46022f6cf9f5ba772aedffeae4743a49e","tid":2342084,"uid":209274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T23:45:07.000Z